      "content": "being \"too much\" just means more friction. more exhaustion. it doesn't actually fix the emptiness. it just feels like i'm endlessly screaming into a void that doesn't even care. i'm just so tired of the struggle. sometimes i feel like the only way to actually find some quiet, some real peace, is to just... stop. to not have to fight anymore.",
